  "description": "A monster created by the coalescing of Electro dispersed throughout nature.\nElectro Slimes can undergo mutations to become a bright yellow. Due to the abundant Electro within its form, it will deliver an electric shock to its surroundings from time to time, and it can even cause nearby Electro Slimes to release electric arcs. This arc lightning will not bounce between purple Electro Slimes, which shows that Electro Slimes have two different polarities.\nOne wonders if some great new science could emerge from the study of such phenomena..."
